Package sik.client.admin

Class Summary
AssignRFIDTagGUI GUI for assigning and un-assigning an RFID tag to a given student
EditMessagesGUI GUI for displaying and editing messages from a student record object
EditMessagesGUIButtonManager Used to handle the complexity of the navigation control buttons of the EditMessages GUI, which generally involves setting specific buttons enabled or disabled depending on the mode and record pointer of the parent GUI
EditMessagesGUIListener A class solely for handling the events made in the Edit Messages GUI
EditResultsGUI A GUI for editing and displaying the assignment results from a student record
EditTimetableGUI A GUI for editing and displaying the assignment results from a student record
OptionsDialog A Dialog for displaying either message or a prompt to the user
RecordsGUI A GUI to navigate through, edit and display the details of student record objects which are stored in a store object
RecordsGUIButtonManager Used to handle the complexity of the navigation control buttons of the Records GUI, which generally involves setting specific buttons enabled or disabled depending on the mode and record pointer of the parent GUI
RecordsGUIListener A class solely for handling the events made in the Records GUI
RunAdminProgram Creates an instance of the Records GUI and runs it
